22/07/2007
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- Luka Karadzic, brother of former Bosnian Serb political leader Radovan Karadzic, said on Friday (July 20th) that police in Montenegro have searched his house, taking CDs, computer disks, family photographs and letters.
Radovan Karadzic has been on the run since 1995, when The Hague war crimes tribunal charged him with genocide, war crimes and crimes against humanity.
(MIA, AP - 20/07/07)
